room_title: Escape room "The Santa Clause" by Great Escape of Central Texas in Killeen
room_address: 4400 E. Central Texas Expy Killeen, TX 76543
room_description: Jack Frost is jealous that he has no holiday or special occasion in his honor. Now his goal is to break into Santa’s home and steal a special snow globe. Once he has the globe his plot is to trick Santa into renouncing his position using the “Escape Clause” where Santa must hold the special globe and say “I wish I’d never been Santa at all” thus sending him back in time and undoing his career as Santa. You and your team of Elves must stop Frost by getting into Santa’s cabin and finding the Globe before Frost does.
